  </sponsors>
  <source>Embil Pharmaceutical Co. Ltd</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This purpose of this study will be to conduct a double-blind, randomized, controlled clinical
      trial to determine the association between intravaginal high dose metronidazole (750mg),
      intravaginal high dose metronidazole combined with an antifungal agent(750mg metronidazole +
      200mg miconazole) and low dose (37.5mg) intravaginal metronidazole, with the rate of
      persistent bacterial vaginosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
